The use of `RxJavaCallAdapterFactory` is only useful if you are trying to return `rx.Observable&lt;Simple&gt;`.

The simplest solution is to return a `Call` as Retrofit expects. You could also write a [`CallAdapter.Factory`][3] if you really need it.

