    double a = Double.longBitsToDouble(0B111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111_1111L);

The largest double is not all bits &#39;1&#39;, the format is the IEEE754. You can play around with a converter to see the effect of the individual bits:
http://www.binaryconvert.com/convert_double.html

